    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-quality specimen of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six benefits from a recent valve adjustment and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the rev range. Power is transmitted via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been meticulously sorted, featuring proactive rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain optimal suspension geometry. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits zero paint flaws and maintains factory-spec panel gaps. A true driver\u2019s car with no mechanical compromises or deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
